data.description: Renovated 3 bedroom home that feels like new construction.  The exterior has new vinyl siding, new roof, new windows, and new heat pump.  The front yard is fenced with large front porch and the rear has a paved drive, fenced and oversized new deck.  Inside has an open feeling from the kitchen to family room with new laminate flooring and plenty of recessed lights.  The kitchen has plenty of new cabinets, new stainless appliances and granite tops.  The 3 bedrooms have new fixtures and laminate flooring.  The full bath has marble flooring and marble surround with new fixtures and vanity.  Set your appointment today so you dont miss this opportunity.
